---
import AboutHeroImage from "../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg";
import Layout from "../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Infrastructure engineer and writer focused on resilient systems and practical thinking."
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		I work at the intersection of platform reliability and long-form
		writing. Most of my engineering effort goes into reducing operational
		fragility, while my writing translates those lessons into ideas other
		builders can use.
	</p>

	<p>
		My favorite projects are the ones where architecture and behavior
		reinforce each other: clear systems, explicit trade-offs, and habits
		that keep teams steady when pressure rises.
	</p>

	<h2>How I work</h2>
	<ul class="about-list">
		<li>Design for recovery paths first, then optimize for speed.</li>
		<li>Prefer measurable reliability gains over abstract complexity.</li>
		<li>
			Document decisions in public so the next iteration starts stronger.
		</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Outside the terminal</h2>
	<p>
		I am building a library of essays on resilience in infrastructure and in
		life. If you care about systems that stay useful under stress, you are
		in the right place.
	</p>
</Layout>
